mainmenu "BLE Environmental Sensor Configuration"

config SENSOR_ENV_INTERVAL_SEC
	int "Environmental sensor sampling interval (seconds)"
	default 900
	range 30 86400
	help
	  Interval in seconds between temperature, humidity, pressure, and battery
	  sensor readings. At 900s (15 min) with 1000 mAh battery this targets
	  months of battery life.

config SENSOR_AIR_QUALITY_DIVISOR
	int "CCS811 read frequency divisor relative to main interval"
	default 2
	range 1 100
	help
	  CCS811 air quality (CO2/TVOC) is read once every N main sensor cycles.
	  With SENSOR_ENV_INTERVAL_SEC=900 and divisor=2, CO2/TVOC updates every
	  30 minutes. Higher values further reduce CCS811 power consumption at
	  the cost of less frequent air quality updates.

source "Kconfig.zephyr"
